{
  "title": "Date-Night Smoky Egyptian Potatoes Tagine",
  "description": "Earthy, fluffy, and char-grilled potatoes in a smoky Egyptian-inspired dish, perfect for a date night. This FODMAP-friendly recipe serves 2 and can be prepared quickly.",
