  "instructions": [
    "Preheat a wok or large skillet to medium-high heat.",
    "Add the olive oil to the wok and swirl to coat the bottom.",
    "Add the potatoes to the wok and cook for 5 minutes, or until they start to brown.",
    "Add the cumin, smoked paprika, salt, and black pepper to the wok and stir to combine.",
    "Add the garlic to the wok and cook for 1 minute, or until fragrant.",
    "Stir in the parsley and cook for another 1-2 minutes, or until the potatoes are tender.",
    "Drizzle the honey over the potatoes and stir to combine.",
    "Stir in the cilantro and cook for 1 minute.",
    "Transfer the potatoes to a serving platter or individual plates.",
    "Serve hot and enjoy!"
  ],
